# Scope for digest/claude-web.md — the repo subset synced into claude.ai
# project knowledge for web/assistant conversations (the non-coding
# surface; coding sessions run in a local harness that reads the repo
# directly and never need the digest).
#
# Globs match against `git ls-files` output, so only tracked files can
# ever be included — gitignored private state (AGENTS.local.md, tasks/,
# user/) is excluded by construction. Lines starting with `!` exclude.
# Contract: topics/web-digest.md

README.md
AGENTS.md
AGENTS.user.md
AGENTS.claude.md
AGENTS.codex.md
AGENTS.grok.md
AGENTS.frontier.md
AGENTS.weak.md
RESEARCH.md
RUNS.md
feature-branch.md
survey-field.md
research-frontier.md
GLOSSARY.md
TOPICS.md
topic-definitions.md
topics/*.md
!topics/*.evidence.md
!topics/*.bearings.md
skills/*/SKILL.md
